5 December 2019 - Minister of Public Works and Infrastructure Patricia de Lille will be launching an initiative by the department in support of the fight against gender-based violence. 5 December 2019 - Former teacher and Media 24 executive Willem Breytenbach, who has been accused of rape by Deon Wiggett appears in court. 5 December 2019 -  Adam Catzavelos with people from the Seth Mazibuko Foundation where he did community service. 5 December 2019 - Almost two years since EFF MP Floyd Shivambu attacked a Netwerk24 journalist in the parliamentary precinct, he’s set to make his first appearance in the Cape Town Magistrate’s court on assault charges. 5 December 2019 - Shumba the lion rests at Drakenstein Lion Park.